<br>
The other day I grouped with 4 mages and another necro in PoV.  all had 61+ pets.  mages were all using air pets for stunns, and of corse LoZ stunns as well.<br>
<br>
Necros would pull, then snare the mob.  the snarer would then kite the mob while the pets killed it.  it was less kitting more of moving, waiting for the mob to stop beeing stuned and take a few steps, then repeat.  then once the mob got to about 2 bubs of life every one chain nuked it to bypass enrage.<br>
<br>
at one point the puller died and we just sicked 5 pets on the mob.  without kiting, and with the mob fighting back as best it could (for some reason it seems every one forgot to nuke as well) the mob died without a pet death, although they all droped down 1/3 or so from enrage.  I guess enrage does not automaticaly hit if the mob is stunned.<br>
<br>
so basicaly, toss the enchanter, get another mage or necro. <p><br>
